name: CuSTOM LISTING : Christmas Cards for Charlotte
Gold Merry Christmas Cards
description:
Personalized, 5"x7" Christmas Cards with envelopes.

Blank Back 
Printed on glossy white stock 
With white envelopes

A percentage of this purchase will go to support Grant & Lindsay Morgan, missionaries in Sweden. (facebook.com/grantandlindsay)

name: Wedding Invitation Suite : Larissa
description:
This sweet rustic invitation suite includes...

50 wedding invitations (5"x7")
50 rsvp cards (3.5"x5")
50 white invitation envelopes*
50 white rsvp envelopes* 

Invitations are printed on 80lb, white paper

Once purchased, please allow 3 days to receive a proof. After proof has been approved invitation will go to print and ship in 10-12 days. Color changes can me made at no extra charge.

*white envelopes are not shown in the photos, if you would like kraft envelopes please contact me for a price.

name: Sweet Tea Kit Tag - Digital File
description:
This tag was created for the Sweet Tea Kit favors at our wedding. 

The hi-res file prints 6 tags to a page and in the photo they are printed on 80lb ivory cardstock.

Tags fit best on box FCBW1 by Nashville Wraps. (nashvillewraps.com)

name: Custom Wedding Invitation Down Payment
description:
This is a down payment for custom wedding invitation design: it includes an initial consultation and 2-3 invitation proofs. (Edits after cost $15.)

(Total design fee not to exceed $200.00.)

Once you have purchased this listing, I will contact you via email to set up a skype meeting or email interview to hear all the details of your big day! You will send the exact wording for your invitations and I will then design 2-3 invitations (based off our conversation) for you to choose from. 

We will move forward with the design of your choice and I will help you have it printed or send you hi-res pdfs for you to print yourself.

name: Custom Calligraphy Down Payment
description:
This is a downpayment for custom calligraphy and will cover 41 envelopes. Calligraphy is $1.20 per envelope. 

Once you have purchased this listing, I will contact you via email to get addresses and/or envelopes if I do not have them already. 

When calligraphy is finished I will create a second listing for the rest of the amount you owe. 

NOTE:: Based on the amount of envelopes and style of calligraphy, please allow 10-14 days turnaround.
